channel.title: X-Machine - Tropical Original
channel.description:
Hello everyone! Today’s track is a “wub-tastic” EDM based song. (Very bad pun)
My songs are also getting deleted when I post new ones due to my soundcloud minutes running out. But that’s ok. I’m fine with out all my other songs. I’ll have to get rid of all the albums though. Oh well.
Here’s my new song!
SoundCloud: [X-Machine - Tropical Original](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/x-machine-tropical-original)
If you would like to remix this track just hit me up and I’ll send you the project link.
